<br>
On land no reindeer can drag more than 135 Kilos. Even if one allow to imagine Santa’s reindeers can drag 10 times as much (at least we assumed they could fly) it would NOT be enough with the usual 9 or 10 reindeers – It would need 214200 well-trained reindeers. This of course will add to the carriage mass to 353430 Ton, which if one compare, is 50 times the French Eiffel-tower mass, included with a few forgotten Japanese tourist’s with their cameras.<br>
<br>
For the fourth:<br>
321000-Ton Christmas gifts, 214200 reindeers and a hell of a large Santa who’s traveling in 3000 Mach will create a very large air-resistance force. The first pair of reindeers will absorb a heat-energy of 14,3 terra joule. Per second. Both of them separately! Both will instantly be transformed to plasma and expose the reindeer’s behind. On less that 4,26 thousands of a second the whole carriage will be transformed to pure radiation. <br>
